July 12, 2018

 - Installing VirtualBox
 - Setting up vagrant 


 - Vagrant command
	- After any changes restart the tomcat server: `sudo service tomcat8 restart`

 - source directory for the Mirage 2 style:
 	- log into `vm` (vagrant ssh) and then navigate to the following directory
 	- `/var/local/vtechworks/src/dspace/dspace/modules/xmlui-mirage2/src/main/webapp/themes/Mirage2/styles`
 	- Update the _style.scss file (nano _style.scss)

 - Make similar to `https://lib.vt.edu/`

 - Vagrant commands:
 	- vagrant up
 	- vagrant destroy
 	- vagrant provision
 	- vagrant ssh (logs into the vm)
 		- sudo service tomcat8 restart
 	
